snippet.title: Visit Australia - Johnny Depp and Amber Heard parody.
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are making amends for not declaring their 2 dogs when visiting Australia in this Visit Australia commercial.

Listen to new episodes of the Anywhere But Here Podcast every fortnight.

Find us online at:

Website - http://www.abhpod.com

Facebook - http://www.facebook.com/abhpod

Twitter - http://www.twitter.com/facebook

email - abhpod@gmail.com

Become a supporter of ABH and get early and exclusive content, find out more at http://www.abhpod.com/support

Note: All video footage in this video, except that of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard,  is used under the creative commons licence. If you are the owner of any of the footage and do not wish for us to use it please send an email to abhpod@gmail.com.

The music in this video is an instrumental version of the song Alive by Empire of the Sun and can be found on YouTube here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pySFQ1Vpiz0

Also note: The video of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard is used in good nature and is intended as a parody, we do not mean to cause any harm. If this is seen as a defamation of their character please also send an email to abhpod@gmail.com
